OL,3,CWhy parents are calling for an under-
OL,4,C16s social media ban
OL,6,FSapna Sanghvi is the regional leader
OL,7,Ffor the smartphone free childhood
OL,8,Fexplains why she supports a ban on
OL,9,Funder-16s using social media.
OL,11,FA mum-of-two is calling on the
OL,12,FGovernment to listen to parents and
OL,13,Fchildren as they launch their
OL,14,Fconsultation on the potential banning
OL,15,Fof social media for children under the
OL,16,Fage of 16.
OL,18,FThe issue will be debated in the House
OL,19,Fof Lords on Wednesday 21 January,
OL,20,Fwhere peers will have the chance to
OL,21,Fvote for or against the ban.
