OL,3,CWhy parents are calling for an under-
OL,4,C16s social media ban
OL,6,FIn December 2025, Australia became the
OL,7,Ffirst country to bring in a ban in
OL,8,FDecember 2025, and the calls for
OL,9,Fsimilar measure in the UK continue to
OL,10,Fgrow.
OL,12,FSapna Sanghvi is a mum-of-two and the
OL,13,Fregional leader for the smartphone
OL,14,Ffree childhood campaign in Manchester.
OL,16,FSapna hopes the Government follows
OL,17,FAustralia's lead and says it's time to
OL,18,Freset the cultural norms.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/16
