OL,3,CWhy parents are calling for an under-
OL,4,C16s social media ban
OL,6,FShe said: "Social media platforms
OL,7,Fweren't designed with children in
OL,8,Fmind, they're very much adult
OL,9,Fenvironments.
OL,11,F"They're addictive by design we didn't
OL,12,Fknow this when they first came out but
OL,13,Fover the years, they've been tweaked
OL,14,Fand tweaked by some of the brightest
OL,15,Fminds in the world, to make sure that
OL,16,Fthey maximise our children's attention
OL,17,Fand therefore their own profits.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/16
