OL,3,CWhy parents are calling for an under-
OL,4,C16s social media ban
OL,6,F"I think what we're seeing now is the
OL,7,Feffect of that and the fact that our
OL,8,Fchildren are showing us that their
OL,9,Fexperience in mental health disorders,
OL,10,Fanxiety, sleep deprivation,
OL,11,Fcyberbullying, myopia, all these
OL,12,Fdifferent things that we didn't really
OL,13,Fenvisage when social media first came
OL,14,Fout."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/16
