OL,3,CWhy parents are calling for an under-
OL,4,C16s social media ban
OL,6,FThe debate comes after 61 Labour MPs
OL,7,Fwrote to the prime minister calling
OL,8,Ffor "urgent action" to raise the
OL,9,Fminimum age for access to social media
OL,10,Fplatforms. ITV News understands at
OL,11,Fleast 66 Labour MPs want the
OL,12,Fgovernment to bring in a social media
OL,13,Fban for under-16s.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/16
