OL,3,CWhy parents are calling for an under-
OL,4,C16s social media ban
OL,6,FThe amendment has already secured the
OL,7,Fsupport of the National Education
OL,8,FUnion (NEU) and 61 Labour MPs, who
OL,9,Fhave written to the Prime Minister
OL,10,Fcalling for "urgent action".
OL,12,FNEU general secretary Daniel Kebede
OL,13,Fsaid the amendment was a "pivotal
OL,14,Fmoment" and urged Sir Keir to show
OL,15,F"leadership" and come out in support
OL,16,Fof a ban.
