OL,3,CWhy parents are calling for an under-
OL,4,C16s social media ban
OL,6,FAt a press conference on Monday
OL,7,Fmorning, Sir Keir would not commit to
OL,8,Fsupporting a ban, but said the
OL,9,FGovernment was "looking at a range of
OL,10,Foptions" and "no options are off the
OL,11,Ftable"
OL,13,FSapna says although individual parents
OL,14,Fmight ban their children from using
OL,15,Fsocial media, it isn't enough to
OL,16,Fprotect them.
