OL,3,CWhy parents are calling for an under-
OL,4,C16s social media ban
OL,6,FShe said: "I worry every day about the
OL,7,Fimpact of social media on my
OL,8,Fchildren's life. I will do everything
OL,9,Fthat I can to keep my children of
OL,10,Fthese platforms and off the devices
OL,11,Fbut the reality is... my child only
OL,12,Fneeds to sit next to another child on
OL,13,Fthe school bus in order to see
OL,14,Fsomething that's inappropriate.
OL,16,F"It's quite upsetting to think that
OL,17,Fyou can't control those environments
OL,18,Ffor your own child."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/16
