OL,3,CWhy parents are calling for an under-
OL,4,C16s social media ban
OL,6,FShe continues: "If your kid is the
OL,7,Fonly one in their friendship group who
OL,8,Fdoesn't have social media, then they
OL,9,Frisk being socially excluded and at
OL,10,Fthat time of life during adolescence,
OL,11,Fbeing socially excluded can be really
OL,12,Fpretty painful, nobody wants that for
OL,13,Ftheir child.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/16
