OL,3,CWhy parents are calling for an under-
OL,4,C16s social media ban
OL,6,F"And so that's why we as parents and
OL,7,Fwe as supporters of the smartphone
OL,8,Ffree childhood, are asking the
OL,9,Fgovernment for their help in raising
OL,10,Fthat age limit, so that we can reset
OL,11,Fthe cultural norm, really, so that it
OL,12,Fbecomes the exception rather than the
OL,13,Frule that children are actually on, on
OL,14,Fthese platforms."
OL,16,FThe mother of a murdered teenager
OL,17,FBrianna Ghey has also urged the Prime
OL,18,FMinister to back a ban on social media
OL,19,Ffor under-16s.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/16
