OL,3,CWhy parents are calling for an under-
OL,4,C16s social media ban
OL,6,FIn a letter to party leaders Sir Keir
OL,7,FStarmer, Kemi Badenoch and Sir Ed
OL,8,FDavey, Esther Ghey said her daughter
OL,9,Fhad had a "social media addiction" and
OL,10,F"desperately wanted to be TikTok
OL,11,Ffamous", putting her "in constant fear
OL,12,Fabout who Brianna might be speaking to
OL,13,Fonline".
OL,15,FShe said: "She developed an eating
OL,16,Fdisorder and was self-harming, and all
OL,17,Fof this was significantly exacerbated
OL,18,Fby the harmful content she was
OL,19,Fconsuming online."
