OL,3,CWhy parents are calling for an under-
OL,4,C16s social media ban
OL,6,FSapna says "I think we need to talk
OL,7,Fabout childhood being protected and
OL,8,Factually the period of time that
OL,9,Fchildren are growing from, you know,
OL,10,Fbeing born to age 16, 17, 18, their
OL,11,Fbrain is developing at a rapid pace
OL,12,Fand it's so important that we protect
OL,13,Fthat time so that children can have a
OL,14,Fhealthy development.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/16
