OL,3,CWhy parents are calling for an under-
OL,4,C16s social media ban
OL,6,F"I think we recognise in many
OL,7,Fdifferent aspects of life that
OL,8,Fchildren should have different roles
OL,9,Fto adults, we apply that to gambling,
OL,10,Falcohol, driving a multitude of
OL,11,Fdifferent things that we know are fine
OL,12,Ffor adults but not fine for children
OL,13,Fand I think we're starting to realise
OL,14,Fthat social media is the same in that
OL,15,Fway.
OL,17,F"Children are still routinely being
OL,18,Fexposed to online pornography, graphic
OL,19,Fviolence, suicide ideation content and
OL,20,Fself-harm videos online.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/16
