OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F397A1769025804
OL,3,CWhy parents are calling for an under-
OL,4,C16s social media ban
OL,6,F"There's no way that an online safety
OL,7,Flesson can stop them from seeing this
OL,8,Fcontent when it's algorithmically
OL,9,Fserved up to them online, on
OL,10,Fplatforms, and in environments where
OL,11,Fthey're not even actively searching
OL,12,Fout this stuff, it's just being
OL,13,Fdelivered to them.
OL,15,F"We need to recognise that children's
OL,16,Fbrains are still developing, at the
OL,17,Fage of 12 or 13, they don't have a
OL,18,Ffully formed prefrontal cortex.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/16
