OL,3,CWhy parents are calling for an under-
OL,4,C16s social media ban
OL,6,F"They can't make rational decisions in
OL,7,Fthe way that we can as adults and so
OL,8,Fit's simply unfair, really, to ask
OL,9,Fthem to manage those platforms
OL,10,Fthemselves and to try and unsee things
OL,11,Fthat they're being delivered on a
OL,12,Fdaily basis."
